<p>Traditional coffee in Shokoladnitsa before departure. We are in sweatshirts! Now it looks crazy!</p>
<div class="blog_pic">
        <img src="images/blog/2016-08-17_pic2.jpg">
</div>
<p>Nicely decorated cafe near our. Mesmerizing.</p>
<div class="blog_pic">
        <img src="images/blog/2016-08-17_pic3.jpg">
</div>
<p>Finally we are in Bergamo. Photo was taken from the plane, so it's a bit bluish-reddish. Flight was awesome! Pobeda airlines are the best ones! The main thing is to take some food with you. But this is the thing we will never forget to do.</p>
<p>As we got outside the plane it's the same feeling we had after arriving at the Podgoritsa: it's crazy hot, very strange trees around and mind blowing mountains!</p>
